OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1780319468
OL,3,CMan arrested after stabbing in
OL,4,CManchester
OL,6,FPolice have arrested a man after
OL,7,Fanother man was stabbed in Manchester
OL,8,Fcity centre on Saturday night.
OL,10,FIt happened on Great Ducie Street just
OL,11,Fafter 11:30pm on Saturday 30 May.
OL,13,FThe victim, a man in his 30s, is being
OL,14,Ftreated in hospital, and police say he
OL,15,Fhas life-threatening injuries.
OL,17,FA 20-year-old man was arrested by
OL,18,Fpolice on nearby Barker Street, on
OL,19,Fsuspicion of section 18 assault and is
OL,20,Fbeing questioned by police.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
