CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1780319468
OL,3,CMan arrested after stabbing in
OL,4,CManchester
OL,6,FChief Inspector Peter Crowe from the
OL,7,FCity of Manchester said: "This swift
OL,8,Fresponse emphasises that Greater
OL,9,FManchester Police have no tolerance
OL,10,Ffor knife crime, and we will work
OL,11,Fproactively to prosecute those who
OL,12,Fchoose to carry knives.
OL,14,F"This was an extremely violent attack,
OL,15,Fand we are working to support the
OL,16,Fvictim and is family at this
OL,17,Fterrifying time.
OL,26,@oD@ZOUvD@AOU
