FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1780319468
OL,3,CMan arrested after stabbing in
OL,4,CManchester
OL,6,F"Detectives are working hard to
OL,7,Funderstand the motive behind this
OL,8,Fattack. However, we do not believe
OL,9,Fthere to be a wider threat to the
OL,10,Fcommunity.
OL,12,F"A scene will remain in place while
OL,13,Four investigation continues, and we
OL,14,Furge anyone with information to come
OL,15,Fforward and speak to us.
OL,17,F"We understand how worrying this will
OL,18,Fbe, and there will be an increased
OL,19,Fpolice presence in the area. I would
OL,20,Fencourage anyone with concerns to talk
OL,21,Fto us."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUyD@AOU}D@GO]
